These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, mirinda, almond-milk, milk, hot-chocolate, cola
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, malaysian, spanish, pakistani, indian, japanese, argentine
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: parkour, handball, ice-hockey, biathlon, badminton, water-polo, rugby
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, car, skateboard, trike, tram, roller, scooter
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is the pakistani##1
 3. the person driving the tram is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the malaysian is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the polish is on the right of the argentine##1
 6. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the indian##1
 8. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the scooter and the japanese##2
 9. the indian is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is parkour is the person drinking milk##1
12. the person drinking milk is the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the spanish##1
14. the japanese is the person driving the skateboard##1
15. the person driving the roller is on the left of the argentine##1
16. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
17. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the spanish##1
18. the person drinking cola is on the right of the indian##1
19. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | water  | hot-chocolate        | milk | mirinda      | almond-milk     | iced-tea      | cola     |
| Nationality   | malaysian | pakistani         | argentine   | polish | japanese    | indian | spanish |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | badminton | parkour | handball | rugby  | water-polo  | biathlon    |
| Transport     | tram  | roller         | motorbike     | car    | skateboard | trike     | scooter     |

